.SH NAME
intel_dsb_prepare \- Allocate, pin and map the DSB command buffer.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" intel_dsb_prepare
.BI "(struct intel_crtc_state *crtc_state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crtc_state" 12
intel_crtc_state structure to prepare associated dsb instance.
